<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.2.5">
<l>nīṇṭā yaivāṉavarkaḷ niṉaintēttik kāṇparitāl</l>
<l>āṇṭā yeṉṟātarikkap paṭuvāykku nāṉaṭimai</l>
<l>pūṇṭē ṉeṉeñciṉuḷḷē pukuntāyaip pōkaloṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>nāṇtā ṉuṉakkoḻintēṉ naṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampīyō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The celestials’ seeing, contemplating, and praising you who became tall</l>
<l rend="indent">is quite rare.</l>
<l>I am bound in service to you who are worshipped [by them] saying,</l>
<l rend="indent">‘You rule [us]’;</l>
<l>I cannot allow [your] going, you who entered into my heart.</l>
<l>For you, I left all shame, O noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
